@startuml Architecture_Tree_Simple
!theme plain

skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor<<gateway>> #FFD700
  BackgroundColor<<domain>> #E3F2FD
  BackgroundColor<<ecu>> #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #333333
  FontSize 12
}

title 시스템 아키텍처 (System Architecture)\nGateway 중심 계층 구조

node "**Central Gateway**" as GW <<gateway>>

node "Infotainment\nDomain" as InfoDomain <<domain>>
node "Body\nDomain" as BodyDomain <<domain>>
node "ADAS\nDomain" as ADASdomain <<domain>>
node "Powertrain\nDomain" as PowerDomain <<domain>>

GW -down-> InfoDomain : CAN 500kbps
GW -down-> BodyDomain : CAN 500kbps
GW -down-> ADASdomain : CAN 500kbps
GW -down-> PowerDomain : CAN 500kbps

' Infotainment Domain ECUs
node "IVI Control ECU" as IVI <<ecu>>
node "vECU (IVI vECU)" as vECU <<ecu>>
node "Cluster ECU" as Cluster <<ecu>>

InfoDomain -down-> IVI
InfoDomain -down-> vECU
InfoDomain -down-> Cluster

' Body Domain ECUs
node "Lighting ECU" as Light <<ecu>>
node "BDC" as BDC <<ecu>>
node "Door Sensors" as Door <<ecu>>

BodyDomain -down-> Light
BodyDomain -down-> BDC
BodyDomain -down-> Door

' ADAS Domain ECUs
node "ADAS ECU" as ADAS <<ecu>>
node "LDW Sensor" as LDW <<ecu>>
node "AEB Sensor" as AEB <<ecu>>

ADASdomain -down-> ADAS
ADASdomain -down-> LDW
ADASdomain -down-> AEB

' Powertrain Domain ECUs
node "Transmission ECU" as Trans <<ecu>>
node "Speed Sensor" as Speed <<ecu>>

PowerDomain -down-> Trans
PowerDomain -down-> Speed

legend right
  |= 구성 |= 설명 |
  | Gateway | 모든 도메인 간 메시지 중계 |
  | Domain | 기능별 ECU 그룹 |
  | ECU | 개별 제어 유닛/센서 |
endlegend

@enduml
